        <mxCell id="stats_box" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#cbd5e1;fillColor=#f8fafc;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Courier New;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 102, 0);&quot;&gt;📊 THỐNG KÊ ERD v1.1&lt;br&gt;────────────────────────&lt;br&gt;Tổng số bảng: 27 (+5 vs v1.0)&lt;br&gt;   Bảng mới: course_approval_requests&lt;br&gt;             parent_report_tokens&lt;br&gt;             analytics_snapshots&lt;br&gt;             lecturer_stats&lt;br&gt;             question_import_batches&lt;br&gt;────────────────────────&lt;br&gt;Quan hệ vẽ: 38 (+8 vs v1.0)&lt;br&gt;Quan hệ 1-0..N: 27 (optional many)&lt;br&gt;Quan hệ 1-N: 6 (mandatory many)&lt;br&gt;Quan hệ 1-0..1: 1 (optional one)&lt;br&gt;────────────────────────&lt;br&gt;FIXES từ BA Review:&lt;br&gt;✅ enrollments→payments: 1-1→1-N&lt;br&gt;✅ questions.subject_id: removed (3NF)&lt;br&gt;✅ courses.current_students: computed&lt;br&gt;✅ integrity_events.event_count: →seq_no&lt;br&gt;✅ ERzeroToMany notation applied&lt;br&gt;✅ 6 missing edges added&lt;br&gt;────────────────────────&lt;br&gt;Bảng UUID PK: 22&lt;br&gt;Bảng SMALLINT PK: 2&lt;br&gt;Soft Delete: 9 bảng&lt;br&gt;Audit Log: standalone table&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="430" width="370" x="2290" y="680" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
